[Despite the increasing number of cases and the geographic spread of
_Salmonella enterica_ serotype Newport (_S._ Newport), there is no report
indicating the vehicle of the outbreak. Initial reports mentioned "take
away" (take out) food, but, so far, the vehicle(s) of the spread, and the
origin of the food, are unclear. - Mod.LL]
